 sections at edges and at internal fold lines. Includes 11 town/village insets (including New Brunswick, Perth Amboy, South Amboy), local business directories, distance table, and illustrations of prominent buildings. LC Land ownership maps, 457 Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. 2 copies"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:39:18.487Z", "group": ["gmd.mar", "catalog-split-10", "catalog", "general-maps", "main-catalog-split-10"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2012593677/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd381/g3813/g3813m/la000457.gif", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd381/g3813/g3813m/la000457.gif#h=155&w=150", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd381:g3813:g3813m:la000457/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=2303&w=2233", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd381:g3813:g3813m:la000457/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=4607&w=4466"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["south amboy", "new brunswick", "middlesex county", "perth amboy", "new jersey", "united states"], "mime_type": ["image/gif", "image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["sheet", "2012593677", "2014-07-09t12:24:15", "2025-06-07t06:10:59.800000"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map"], "partof": ["cultural landscapes", "county landownership maps", "catalog", "geography and map division"], "score": 57.048836, "shelf_id": "G3813.M5 1861 .W3 G3813.M5 1861 .W3 Copy 2", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["south amboy", "real property", "middlesex county (n.j.)", "new brunswick", "middlesex county", "villages", "new brunswick (n.j.)", "landowners", "perth amboy", "new jersey", "cities and towns", "perth amboy (n.j.)", "south amboy (n.j.)", "united states", "maps"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T16:07:16.015Z", "title": "Map of the county of Middlesex, New Jersey : from actual surveys", "type": ["cartographic"], 